sql:
SELECT department, COUNT(employee_id) AS employee_count
FROM employee
GROUP BY department;

external_knowledge:
- "Shining stars among the products" refers to the top products based on their total quantity in stock; 
- "Swimming in abundance" means the product categories have an above-average quantity in stock compared to all categories;
- "Golden customers" refers to customers with a high number of orders and total spending;
- "Pair each of these stars with their potential patrons" means to cross-join the top products and top customers, indicating a potential relationship or market analysis interest.

